    <text type="note" xml:lang="ru" xml:id="letter-09037">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when-custom="1787-09-19">1787 г. 19 сентября.</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Выправься пожалуй: <orgName ref="orgs.xml#sena01">сенатом</orgName> сняты ли генерал- губернаторския и губернаторския прещения о невывозе хлеба из губерний, и когда посланы указы; а буде не посланы, то напомните о сем <persName ref="people.xml#kol03">Колокольцову</persName> 
                <note type="editorial">
                    <persName ref="people.xml#kol03">Fedor Mikhailovich Kolokol'tsov</persName> was Ober Procurator of the <orgName ref="orgs.xml#sena01">Senate</orgName> at that time (
                    <bibl>
                        <title ref="works.xml#sobstv02">Sobstvennoruchnyia pis'ma i zapiski imperatritsy Ekateriny II k A. V. Khranovitskomu, 1783-1793</title>,
                        <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 21.</biblScope>)
                    </bibl>
                </note> от меня
                <note type="editorial">
                    According to A.V. Khrapovitskii's diary, on <date when-custom="1787-09-20">September 20 1787</date> he was ordered to prepare the decree on free trade of bread within the <placeName ref="places.xml#rus01">Russian Empire</placeName>, following the embargo imposed by several Governor-Generals (
                    <bibl>
                        <title ref="works.xml#dnevni02">Dnevnik A.V. Khrapovitskago s 18 ianvaria 1782 po 17 sentiabria 1793 goda</title>
                        , <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 29.</biblScope>
                    </bibl>
                    ).
                </note>
            </p>
        </body>
